description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Health Care Support Workers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Exciting times ahead….&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are expanding our workforce which brings incredible opportunities for YOU&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;We have a variety of clinical areas to choose from which means you can find a place to enhance your skills and progress your career.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Trust provides support for all healthcare support workers to complete mandatory training, including the Care Certificate. We also offer a progression pathway for the right candidate, giving training and support to advance to more senior positions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;By joining our teams you will be able to access our fabulous benefits including:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;•Being part of a winning team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;•Joining our health and wellbeing programme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;•Developing under our career progression pathway&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This post will be based at Royal Papworth Hospital Cambridge Biomedical Campus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;What our nurses say…..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“We are proud of the work we do caring for our patients through a multitude of invasive and non- invasive cardiac procedures and investigations”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;“We are in incredible team and we are committed to giving our all to support the best patient outcome”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“Cardiology is a stimulating and thrilling place to work”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;What our patients say…..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“During the operation all of the doctors and nurses assured me of the safe process which was completed as planned. Excellent 5 star job done”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;“The facilities at Royal Papworth are superb - a wonderful hospital. The staff - all staff, make Royal Papworth a top class experience”&lt;span&gt;“Staff were friendly, welcoming, helpful and professional. I felt relaxed and at ease during my visit because of the superb way I was treated by all staff - A credit to Royal Papworth and the NHS”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Regular shortlisting takes place and you will be contacted for a Skype interview if you are shortlisted for interview.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
